<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body { background-color: #101010; color: #fff; font-family: Arial,
      sans-serif; padding: 20px; margin: 0; } .container { max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto; background-color: #1a1a1a; border-radius: 8px; overflow:
      hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); } .header {
      background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #2B7FFF; padding: 20px; text-align:
      center; border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #fff; } .content {
      padding: 20px; background-color: #262626; } .content p { margin: 0 0 16px;
      line-height: 1.6; color: #e0e0e0; } .notice-section { background-color:
      #1a1a1a; color: #e0e0e0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px
      0; border-left: 4px solid #2B7FFF; } .notice-section h2 { color: #2B7FFF;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 18px; } .reason-section { background-color:
      #1a1a1a; color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px
      0; border-left: 4px solid #5BA3FF; } .reason-section h3 { color: #5BA3FF;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; } .reason-text { background-color:
      #333; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 0; font-style:
      italic; color: #ccc; } .action-section { background-color: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid
      #2B7FFF; } .action-section h3 { color: #2B7FFF; margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      font-size: 16px; } .contact-section { background-color: #1a1a1a; padding:
      20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; }
      .contact-button { display: inline-block; background-color: #2B7FFF; color:
      #1a1a1a !important; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0; text-align: center;
      } .contact-button:hover { background-color: #5BA3FF; } .footer {
      text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #aaa;
      background-color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; } .footer p { margin: 0; } .footer a {
      color: #2B7FFF; text-decoration: none; } .closing { text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #1a1a1a; border-radius:
      8px; } .team-signature { font-weight: bold; color: #2B7FFF; margin-top:
      10px; } .tagline { font-style: italic; color: #aaa; margin-top: 5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Chat Access Update</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="notice-section">
          <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
          <p>We hope this message finds you well. We're writing to inform you
            about a temporary change to your account access.</p>
          <p>Your access to the chat functionality has been temporarily
            restricted. This action was taken to ensure the safety and integrity
            of our community platform.</p>
          <p>Please note that this restriction only affects the chat feature and
            does not impact your access to course content or other platform
            features.</p>
        </div>

        {{#if reason}}
          <div class="reason-section">
            <h3>Reason for Restriction</h3>
            <div class="reason-text">
              "{{reason}}"
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="closing">
          <p>Thank you for your understanding and continued participation in our
            community.</p>
          <p>Grace and peace,</p>
          <p class="team-signature">The Church Planting Institute Team</p>
          <p class="tagline">Empowering shepherds for global impact</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact
          <a target="_blank" href="mailto:bluehancedigital@gmail.com">our
            support team.</a>
        </p>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} Church Planting Institute. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>